700586,134,665,2,11,1,36,4,146. Tatiye {candūpamā}ti candasadisā hutvā. 
700587,134,665,12,14,1,19,2,Kiṃ parimaṇḍalatāya? 
700588,134,665,15,65,1,335,46,"No, apica kho yathā cando gaganatalaṃ pakkhandamāno na kenaci saddhiṃ santhavaṃ vā sinehaṃ vā ālayaṃ vā nikantiṃ vā patthanaṃ vā pariyuṭṭhānaṃ vā karoti, na ca na hoti mahājanassa piyo manāpo, tumhepi evaṃ kenaci saddhiṃ santhavādīnaṃ akaraṇena bahujanassa piyā manāpā candūpamā hutvā khattiyakulādīni cattāri kulāni upasaṅkamathāti attho. "
700589,134,665,66,86,1,166,18,"Apica yathā cando andhakāraṃ vidhamati, ālokaṃ pharati, evaṃ kilesandhakāravidhamanena ñāṇālokapharaṇena cāpi candūpamā hutvāti evamādīhipi nayehi ettha attho daṭṭhabbo. "
700590,134,666,2,16,1,112,13,"Apakasseva kāyaṃ apakassa cittan ti teneva santhavādīnaṃ akaraṇena kāyañca cittañca apakassitvā, apanetvāti attho. "
700591,134,666,17,34,1,97,14,"Yo hi bhikkhu araññepi na vasati, kāmavitakkādayopi vitakketi, ayaṃ neva kāyaṃ apakassati, na cittaṃ. "
700592,134,666,35,51,1,93,13,"Yo hi araññepi kho viharati, kāmavitakkādayo pana vitakketi, ayaṃ kāyameva apakassati, na cittaṃ. "
700593,134,666,52,69,1,90,13,"Yo gāmante vasati , kāmavitakkādayopi kho na ca vitakketi, ayaṃ cittameva apakassati, na kāyaṃ. "
