700596,134,667,2,11,1,62,7,"{Niccanavakā}ti niccaṃ navakāva, āgantukasadisā eva hutvāti attho. "
700597,134,667,12,83,1,467,55,"Āgantuko hi paṭipāṭiyā sampattagehaṃ pavisitvā sace naṃ gharasāmikā disvā,‘‘ amhākaṃ puttabhātaro vippavāsaṃ gatā evaṃ vicariṃsū’’ ti anukampamānā nisīdāpetvā bhojenti, bhuttamattoyeva‘‘ tumhākaṃ bhājanaṃ gaṇhathā’’ ti uṭṭhāya pakkamati, na tehi saddhiṃ santhavaṃ vā karoti, na kiccakaraṇīyāni vā saṃvidahati, evaṃ tumhepi paṭipāṭiyā sampattagharaṃ pavisitvā yaṃ iriyāpathesu pasannā manussā denti, taṃ gahetvā chinnasanthavā, tesaṃ kiccakaraṇīye abyāvaṭā hutvā nikkhamathāti dīpeti. "
