701508,134,845,38,46,1,79,7,{Ahaṅkāramamaṅkāramānānusayā}ti ahaṃkāradiṭṭhi ca mamaṃkārataṇhā ca mānānusayā ca. 
701509,134,845,47,59,1,74,11,Na {hontī}ti ete kilesā kathaṃ jānantassa etesu vatthūsu na hontīti pucchati. 
701510,134,845,60,68,1,68,7,Sammappaññāya {passatī}ti saha vipassanāya maggapaññāya suṭṭhu passati. 
701511,134,845,69,70,1,10,1,Ekādasamaṃ.
701512,134,846,2,4,1,19,2,12 . Apagatasuttavaṇṇanā 
701513,134,847,2,17,1,89,10,201. Dvādasame ahaṅkāramamaṅkāramānāpagatan ti ahaṃkārato ca mamaṃkārato ca mānato ca apagataṃ. 
701514,134,847,18,24,1,53,6,Vidhā samatikkantan ti mānakoṭṭhāse suṭṭhu atikkantaṃ. 
701515,134,847,25,34,1,71,8,"Santaṃ suvimuttan ti kilesavūpasamena santaṃ, kileseheva suṭṭhu vimuttaṃ. "
701516,134,847,35,37,1,18,2,Sesaṃ uttānamevāti. 
701517,134,847,38,39,1,10,1,Dvādasamaṃ. 
701518,134,848,2,4,1,12,2,Dutiyo vaggo. 
701519,134,849,2,6,1,28,3,Dvīsupi asekkhabhūmi kathitā. 
701520,134,849,7,14,1,56,6,"Paṭhamo panettha āyācantassa desito, dutiyo anāyācantassa. "
701521,134,849,15,21,1,75,6,Sakalepi pana rāhulasaṃyutte therassa vimuttiparipācanīyadhammāva kathitāti. 
701522,134,850,2,4,1,30,2,Rāhulasaṃyuttavaṇṇanā niṭṭhitā. 
701523,134,851,1,4,1,17,1,8. Lakkhaṇasaṃyuttaṃ
701524,134,852,2,4,1,12,2,1 . Paṭhamavaggo
701525,134,853,2,4,1,17,2,1 . Aṭṭhisuttavaṇṇanā 
701526,134,854,2,28,1,190,17,"202. Lakkhaṇasaṃyutte yvāyaṃ āyasmā ca {lakkhaṇo}ti lakkhaṇatthero vutto, esa jaṭilasahassabbhantare ehibhikkhūpasampadāya upasampanno ādittapariyāyāvasāne arahattaṃ patto eko mahāsāvakoti veditabbo. "
701527,134,854,29,46,1,119,12,"Yasmā panesa lakkhaṇasampannena sabbākāraparipūrena brahmasamena attabhāvena samannāgato, tasmā‘‘ lakkhaṇo’’ ti saṅkhaṃ gato. "
701528,134,854,47,56,1,86,9,Mahāmoggallāno pana pabbajitadivasato sattame divase arahattaṃ patto dutiyo aggasāvako. 
701529,134,855,2,12,1,71,8,"Sitaṃ {pātvākāsī}ti mandahasitaṃ pātuakāsi, pakāsayi dassesīti vuttaṃ hoti. "
701530,134,855,13,19,1,38,6,Kiṃ pana disvā thero sitaṃ pātvākāsīti? 
701531,134,855,20,29,1,76,9,Upari pāḷiyaṃ āgataṃ aṭṭhikasaṅkhalikaṃ ekaṃ petaloke nibbattaṃ sattaṃ disvā. 
701532,134,855,30,37,1,44,6,"Tañca kho dibbena cakkhunā, na pasādacakkhunā. "
701533,134,855,38,45,1,54,7,Pasādacakkhussa hi ete attabhāvā na āpāthaṃ āgacchanti. 
701534,134,855,46,55,1,71,9,Evarūpaṃ pana attabhāvaṃ disvā kāruññe kattabbe kasmā sitaṃ pātvākāsīti? 
701535,134,855,56,62,1,52,6,Attano ca buddhañāṇassa ca sampattiṃ samanussaraṇato. 
701536,134,855,63,91,1,158,22,"Tañhi disvā thero‘‘ adiṭṭhasaccena nāma puggalena paṭilabhitabbā evarūpā attabhāvā mutto ahaṃ, lābhā vata me, suladdhaṃ vata me’’ ti attano ca sampattiṃ anussaritvā–"
701537,134,855,92,129,1,228,26,"‘‘ aho buddhassa bhagavato ñāṇasampatti,‘ yo kammavipāko, bhikkhave, acinteyyo na cintetabbo’ ti desesi, paccakkhaṃ vata katvā buddhā desenti, suppaṭividdhā buddhānaṃ dhammadhātū’’ ti evaṃ buddhañāṇasampattiñca anussaritvā sitaṃ pātvākāsīti. "
701538,134,856,2,12,1,64,8,"Atha lakkhaṇatthero kasmā na addasa, kimassa dibbacakkhu natthīti? "
701539,134,856,13,27,1,80,11,"No natthi, mahāmoggallāno pana āvajjento addasa, itaro pana anāvajjanena na addasa. "
701540,134,856,28,55,1,147,22,"Yasmā pana khīṇāsavā nāma na akāraṇā sitaṃ karonti, tasmā taṃ lakkhaṇatthero pucchi ko nu kho, āvuso moggallāna, hetu, ko paccayo sitassa {pātukammāyā}ti? "
701541,134,856,56,80,1,145,19,"Thero pana yasmā yehi ayaṃ upapatti sāmaṃ adiṭṭhā, te dussaddhāpayā honti, tasmā bhagavantaṃ sakkhiṃ katvā byākātukāmatāya akālo kho, {āvuso}tiādimāha. "
701542,134,856,81,91,1,65,8,"Tato bhagavato santike puṭṭho idhāhaṃ, {āvuso}tiādinā nayena byākāsi. "
701543,134,857,2,8,1,65,6,Tattha aṭṭhikasaṅkhalikan ti setaṃ nimmaṃsalohitaṃ aṭṭhisaṅghātaṃ. 
701544,134,857,9,21,1,91,11,Gijjhāpi kākāpi {kulalāpī}ti etepi yakkhagijjhā ceva yakkhakākā ca yakkhakulalā ca paccetabbā. 
701545,134,857,22,29,1,60,7,Pākatikānaṃ pana gijjhādīnaṃ āpāthampi etaṃ rūpaṃ nāgacchati. 
701546,134,857,30,35,1,49,4,Anupatitvā {anupatitvā}ti anubandhitvā anubandhitvā. 
701547,134,857,36,48,1,100,11,{Vitudentī}ti asidhārūpamehi tikhiṇehi lohatuṇḍakehi vijjhitvā vijjhitvā ito cito ca caranti gacchanti. 
701548,134,857,49,65,1,109,14,"Sā sudaṃ aṭṭassaraṃ {karotī}ti ettha sudan ti nipāto, sā aṭṭhikasaṅkhalikā aṭṭassaraṃ āturassaraṃ karotīti attho. "
701549,134,857,66,77,1,115,10,"Akusalavipākānubhavanatthaṃ kira yojanappamāṇāpi tādisā attabhāvā nibbattanti, pasādussadā ca honti pakkagaṇḍasadisā. "
701550,134,857,78,84,1,65,6,Tasmā sā aṭṭhikasaṅkhalikā balavavedanāturā tādisaṃ saddamakāsīti. 
701551,134,858,2,35,1,213,26,"Evañca pana vatvā puna āyasmā mahāmoggallāno‘‘ vaṭṭagāmisattā nāma evarūpā attabhāvā na muccantī’’ ti sattesu kāruññaṃ paṭicca uppannaṃ dhammasaṃvegaṃ dassento tassa mayhaṃ, āvuso, etadahosi acchariyaṃ vata {bho}tiādimāha. "
701552,134,858,36,50,1,94,10,"Tato bhagavā therassa ānubhāvaṃ pakāsento cakkhubhūtā vata, bhikkhave , sāvakā {viharantī}tiādimāha. "
701553,134,858,51,65,1,122,13,"Tattha cakkhu bhūtaṃ jātaṃ uppannaṃ etesanti cakkhubhūtā, bhūtacakkhukā uppannacakkhukā cakkhuṃ uppādetvā viharantīti attho. "
701554,134,858,66,69,1,23,3,Dutiyapadepi eseva nayo. 
701555,134,858,70,78,1,43,6,Yatra hi {nāmā}ti ettha {yatrā}ti kāraṇavacanaṃ. 
701556,134,858,79,96,1,108,15,"Tatrāyaṃ atthayojanā– yasmā nāma sāvakopi evarūpaṃ ñassati vā dakkhati vā sakkhiṃ vā karissati, tasmā avocumha–"
701557,134,858,97,117,1,88,11,"‘‘ cakkhubhūtā vata, bhikkhave, sāvakā viharanti, ñāṇabhūtā vata, bhikkhave, sāvakā viharantī’’ ti. "
701558,134,858,118,143,1,207,22,"Pubbeva me so, bhikkhave, satto {diṭṭho}ti bodhimaṇḍe sabbaññutaññāṇapaṭivedhena appamāṇesu cakkavāḷesu appamāṇe sattanikāye bhavagatiyoniṭhitinivāse ca paccakkhaṃ karontena mayā pubbeva so satto diṭṭhoti vadati. "
701559,134,859,2,14,1,82,9,{Goghātako}ti gāvo vadhitvā aṭṭhito maṃsaṃ mocetvā vikkiṇitvā jīvikaṃ kappanakasatto. 
701560,134,859,15,23,1,83,7,Tasseva kammassa {vipākāvasesenā}ti tassa nānācetanāhi āyūhitassa aparāpariyakammassa. 
701561,134,859,24,61,1,258,31,"Tatra hi yāya cetanāya narake paṭisandhi janitā, tassā vipāke parikkhīṇe avasesakammaṃ vā kammanimittaṃ vā ārammaṇaṃ katvā puna petādīsu paṭisandhi nibbattati, tasmā sā paṭisandhi kammasabhāgatāya ārammaṇasabhāgatāya vā‘‘ tasseva kammassa vipākāvaseso’’ ti vuccati. "
701562,134,859,62,66,1,25,4,Ayañca satto evaṃ uppanno. 
701563,134,859,67,68,1,6,1,Tenāha–
701564,134,859,69,77,1,34,4,‘‘ tasseva kammassa vipākāvasesenā’’ ti. 
701565,134,859,78,87,1,80,9,Tassa kira narakā cavanakāle nimmaṃsakatānaṃ gunnaṃ aṭṭhirāsiyeva nimittaṃ ahosi. 
701566,134,859,88,98,1,83,10,So paṭicchannampi taṃ kammaṃ viññūnaṃ pākaṭaṃ viya karonto aṭṭhisaṅkhalikapeto jāto. 
701567,134,859,99,100,1,8,1,Paṭhamaṃ.
