701590,134,871,18,31,1,58,9,So kira‘‘ amukasmiṃ padese viddho maratī’’ ti ñatvāva vijjhati. 
701591,134,871,32,44,1,117,12,Tassevaṃ jīvikaṃ kappetvā narake uppannassa tato pakkāvasesena idhūpapattikāle usunā vijjhanabhāvoyeva nimittaṃ ahosi. 
