701605,134,876,2,4,1,21,2,10 . Kumbhaṇḍasuttavaṇṇanā 
701606,134,877,2,10,1,48,3,211. Aṇḍabhārivatthusmiṃ {gāmakūṭako}ti vinicchayāmacco. 
701607,134,877,11,17,1,63,6,Tassa kammasabhāgatāya kumbhamattā mahāghaṭappamāṇā aṇḍā ahesuṃ. 
701608,134,877,18,39,1,152,20,"So hi yasmā raho paṭicchanne ṭhāne lañjaṃ gahetvā kūṭavinicchayena pākaṭaṃ dosaṃ karonto sāmike assāmike akāsi, tasmāssa rahassaṃ aṅgaṃ pākaṭaṃ nibbattaṃ. "
701609,134,877,40,54,1,107,13,"Yasmā daṇḍaṃ paṭṭhapento paresaṃ asayhaṃ bhāraṃ āropesi, tasmāssa rahassaṃ aṅgaṃ asayhabhāro hutvā nibbattaṃ. "
701610,134,877,55,72,1,117,15,"Yasmā yasmiṃ ṭhāne ṭhitena samena bhavitabbaṃ, tasmiṃ ṭhatvā visamo ahosi, tasmāssa rahassaṅge visamā nisajjāva ahosīti. "
