704652,136,48,56,77,1,109,14,"‘‘ Tātā, ayuttaṃ pāṭibhogaṃ dāpetha, na sakkā evaṃ pāṭibhogaṃ dātuṃ, tiṇagge ussāvabindusadisaṃ sattānaṃ jīvitan’’ ti."
704653,136,48,78,97,1,70,12,"‘‘ No ce, deva, pāṭibhogaṃ detha, mayaṃ antarā matā kiṃ kusalaṃ karissāmā’’ ti?"
