705757,136,325,2,53,1,346,42,"Tamenaṃ evaṃ vadeyyun ti channaṃ gharānaṃ ekagharepi kiñci alabhitvā gāmamajjhe eko sandacchāyo rukkho atthi, tattha vaṅkaphalakaṃ atthataṃ disvā,‘‘ idha tāva nisīdissāmī’’ ti gantvā, tattha nisinnaṃ mandamandena vātena bījiyamānaṃ tattakamattampi sukhaṃ santato assādayamānaṃ, tamenaṃ purisaṃ kecideva atthacarakā bahi pavattiṃ ñatvā āgatā evaṃ vadeyyuṃ. "
