706168,136,418,59,93,1,205,21,"Upāsakā‘‘ dhammassavanaṃ kāressāmā’’ ti vihāramaggaṃ sodhetvā, sappitelādīni ādāya, mahātheraṃ upasaṅkamitvā,‘‘ bhante, dhammassavanaṃ kāressāma, dhammakathikānaṃ vicārethā’’ ti vatvā punadivase āgantvā dhammaṃ suṇanti. "
706169,136,419,2,9,1,91,7,Nevāsikatthero āgantukānaṃ pattacīvarāni paṭisāmento antogabbheyeva divasabhāgaṃ vītināmeti. 
706170,136,419,10,26,1,106,14,"Divākathiko uṭṭhito sarabhāṇako ghaṭena udakaṃ vamento viya sarabhāṇaṃ bhaṇitvā uṭṭhito, tampi so na jānāti. "
706171,136,419,27,39,1,78,11,"Rattikathiko sāgaraṃ khobhento viya rattiṃ kathetvā uṭṭhito, tampi so na jānāti. "
706172,136,419,40,48,1,50,7,"Paccūsakathiko kathetvā uṭṭhāsi, tampi so na jānāti. "
706173,136,419,49,64,1,110,12,"Pātova pana uṭṭhāya mukhaṃ dhovitvā, therānaṃ pattacīvarāni upanāmetvā, bhikkhācāraṃ upagacchanto mahātheraṃ āha –"
706174,136,419,65,107,1,233,31,"‘‘ bhante, divākathiko kataraṃ jātakaṃ nāma kathesi, sarabhāṇako kataraṃ suttaṃ nāma bhaṇi, rattikathiko kataraṃ dhammakathaṃ nāma kathesi, paccūsakathiko kataraṃ jātakaṃ nāma kathesi, khandhā nāma kati, dhātuyo nāma kati, āyatanā nāma katī’’ ti. "
706175,136,419,108,126,1,157,17,Evarūpo ekaṃ dve saṃvaccharāni atikkamitvā bhikkhudassanañceva dhammassavanañca labhantopi oghe āgate udakena sakiṃ vā dvikkhattuṃ vā temitarukkhasadiso hoti. 
706176,136,419,127,144,1,147,17,So evaṃ saṅghadassanato ca dhammassavanato ca paṭikkamma dūre vasanto ariyamaggaṃ otaritvā samādhikulle nisinno nibbānasāgaraṃ pāpuṇituṃ na sakkoti. 
706177,136,420,2,10,1,79,8,Majjhe gaṅgāya dīpake jāto mudurukkho viya madhurassarabhāṇakapuggalo veditabbo. 
706178,136,420,11,35,1,244,22,"So hi abhiññātāni abhiññātāni vessantarādīni jātakāni uggaṇhitvā, dullabhabhikkhudassanaṃ paccantaṃ gantvā, tattha dhammakathāya pasāditahadayena janena upaṭṭhiyamāno attānaṃ uddissa kate sampannapupphaphalarukkhe nandanavanābhirāme vihāre vasati. "
706179,136,420,36,50,1,96,11,"Athassa bhārahārabhikkhū taṃ pavattiṃ sutvā,‘‘ asuko kira evaṃ upaṭṭhākesu paṭibaddhacitto viharati. "
706180,136,420,51,78,1,200,22,"Paṇḍito bhikkhu paṭibalo buddhavacanaṃ vā uggaṇhituṃ, kammaṭṭhānaṃ vā manasikātuṃ, ānetvā tena saddhiṃ asukattherassa santike dhammaṃ uggaṇhissāma, asukattherassa santike kammaṭṭhānan’’ ti tattha gacchanti. "
706181,136,421,2,33,1,130,19,"So tesaṃ vattaṃ katvā sāyanhasamayaṃ vihāracārikaṃ nikkhantehi tehi‘‘ imaṃ, āvuso, cetiyaṃ tayā kāritan’’ ti puṭṭho,‘‘ āma, bhante’’ ti vadati."
706182,136,421,34,52,1,80,12,"‘‘ Ayaṃ bodhi, ayaṃ maṇḍapo, idaṃ uposathāgāraṃ, esā aggisālā, ayaṃ caṅkamo tayā kārito. "
706183,136,421,53,63,1,61,8,Ime rukkhe ropāpetvā tayā nandanavanābhirāmo vihāro kārito’’ ti.
706184,136,421,64,74,1,20,4,"‘‘ Āma, bhante’’ ti, vadati. "
706185,136,422,2,8,1,48,6,So sāyaṃ therupaṭṭhānaṃ gantvā vanditvā pucchati–
706186,136,422,9,19,1,25,4,"‘‘ kasmā, bhante, āgatatthā’’ ti?"
706187,136,422,20,50,1,183,21,"‘‘ Āvuso, taṃ ādāya gantvā, asukattherassa santike dhammaṃ uggaṇhitvā, asukattherassa santike kammaṭṭhānaṃ, asukasmiṃ nāma araññe samaggā samaṇadhammaṃ karissāmāti iminā kāraṇena āgatamhā’’ ti. "
706188,136,422,51,71,1,119,15,"Sādhu, bhante, tumhe nāma mayhaṃ atthāya āgatā, ahampi ciranivāsena idha ukkaṇṭhito gacchāmi, pattacīvaraṃ gaṇhāmi, bhanteti. "
706189,136,422,72,82,1,76,8,"Āvuso, sāmaṇeradaharā maggakilantā, ajja vasitvā sve pacchābhattaṃ gamissāmāti. "
706190,136,422,83,91,1,55,7,"Sādhu, bhanteti punadivase tehi saddhiṃ piṇḍāya pavisati. "
706191,136,422,92,115,1,135,17,Gāmavāsino‘‘ amhākaṃ ayyo bahū āgantuke bhikkhū gahetvā āgato’’ ti āsanāni paññāpetvā yāguṃ pāyetvā sukhanisinnakathaṃ sutvā bhattaṃ adaṃsu. 
706192,136,422,116,135,1,103,12,"Therā‘‘ tvaṃ, āvuso, anumodanaṃ katvā nikkhama, mayaṃ udakaphāsukaṭṭhāne bhattakiccaṃ karissāmā’’ ti nikkhantā. "
