706201,136,423,68,78,1,56,8,Daharo‘‘ tumhesu evaṃ dukkhitesu ahaṃ gantvā kiṃ karissāmi? 
706202,136,423,79,86,1,33,5,There uyyojessāmī’’ ti vihāraṃ gato. 
706203,136,424,2,26,1,113,15,"Therāpi katabhattakiccā pattacīvarāni gahetvā nisinnā taṃ disvāva,‘‘ kiṃ, āvuso, cirāyasi, divā hoti, gacchāmā’’ ti āhaṃsu. "
706204,136,424,27,58,1,246,24,"Āma, bhante, tumhe sukhitā, asukagehassa iṭṭhakāmūlaṃ ṭhitasaṇṭhāneneva ṭhitaṃ, asukagehādīnaṃ cittakammamūlādīni atthi, gatassāpi me cittavikkhepo bhavissati, tumhe purato gantvā asukavihāre cīvaradhovanarajanādīni karotha, ahaṃ tattha sampāpuṇissāmīti. "
