709797,137,533,2,24,1,141,13,"478. Aṭṭhame kattha ca, bhikkhave, saddhindriyaṃ daṭṭhabbaṃ, catūsu {sotāpattiyaṅgesū}tiādi imesaṃ indriyānaṃ savisaye jeṭṭhakabhāvadassanatthaṃ vuttaṃ. "
709798,137,533,25,52,1,178,21,"Yathā hi cattāro seṭṭhiputtā rājāti rājapañcamesu sahāyesu‘‘ nakkhattaṃ kīḷissāmā’’ ti vīthiṃ otiṇṇesu ekassa seṭṭhiputtassa gehaṃ gatakāle itare cattāro tuṇhī nisīdanti, gehasāmikova–"
709799,137,533,53,67,1,79,9,"‘‘ imesaṃ khādanīyaṃ bhojanīyaṃ detha, gandhamālālaṅkārādīni dethā’’ ti gehe vicāreti. "
709800,137,533,68,81,1,89,10,"Dutiyassa, tatiyassa, catutthassa gehaṃ gatakāle itare cattāro tuṇhī nisīdanti, gehasāmikova–"
709801,137,533,82,96,1,79,9,"‘‘ imesaṃ khādanīyaṃ bhojanīyaṃ detha, gandhamālālaṅkārādīni dethā’’ ti gehe vicāreti. "
709802,137,533,97,112,1,101,14,"Atha sabbapacchā rañño gehaṃ gatakāle kiñcāpi rājā sabbattha issaro, imasmiṃ pana kāle attano geheyeva–"
709803,137,533,113,127,1,79,9,"‘‘ imesaṃ khādanīyaṃ bhojanīyaṃ detha, gandhamālālaṅkārādīni dethā’’ ti gehe vicāreti. "
709804,137,533,128,162,1,296,31,"Evameva saddhāpañcamakesu indriyesu tesu sahāyesu ekato vīthiṃ otarantesu viya ekārammaṇe uppajjamānesupi yathā paṭhamassa gehe itare cattāro tuṇhī nisīdanti, gehasāmikova vicāreti, evaṃ sotāpattiyaṅgāni patvā adhimokkhalakkhaṇaṃ saddhindriyameva jeṭṭhakaṃ hoti pubbaṅgamaṃ, sesāni tadanvayāni honti. "
709805,137,533,163,186,1,185,20,"Yathā dutiyassa gehe itare cattāro tuṇhī nisīdanti, gehasāmikova vicāreti, evaṃ sammappadhānāni patvā paggahalakkhaṇaṃ vīriyindriyameva jeṭṭhakaṃ hoti pubbaṅgamaṃ, sesāni tadanvayāni honti. "
709806,137,533,187,210,1,184,20,"Yathā tatiyassa gehe itare cattāro tuṇhī nisīdanti, gehasāmikova vicāreti, evaṃ satipaṭṭhānāni patvā upaṭṭhānalakkhaṇaṃ satindriyameva jeṭṭhakaṃ hoti pubbaṅgamaṃ, sesāni tadanvayāni honti. "
709807,137,533,211,234,1,188,20,"Yathā catutthassa gehe itare cattāro tuṇhī nisīdanti, gehasāmikova vicāreti, evaṃ jhānavimokkhe patvā avikkhepalakkhaṇaṃ samādhindriyameva jeṭṭhakaṃ hoti pubbaṅgamaṃ, sesāni tadanvayāni honti. "
709808,137,533,235,262,1,209,24,"Sabbapacchā rañño gehaṃ gatakāle pana yathā itare cattāro tuṇhī nisīdanti, rājāva gehe vicāreti, evameva ariyasaccāni patvā pajānanalakkhaṇaṃ paññindriyameva jeṭṭhakaṃ hoti pubbaṅgamaṃ, sesāni tadanvayāni hontīti."
