709884,137,562,2,23,1,141,13,493. Tatiye anaññātaññassāmītindriyan ti‘‘ anamatagge saṃsāre ajānitapubbaṃ dhammaṃ jānissāmī’’ ti paṭipannassa sotāpattimaggakkhaṇe uppannaṃ indriyaṃ. 
