709892,137,564,14,46,1,313,25,"Samattāni hi pañcindriyāni arahattamaggassa vipassanindriyāni nāma honti, tato mudutarāni antarāparinibbāyissa vipassanindriyāni, tato mudutarāni upahaccaparinibbāyissa, tato mudutarāni asaṅkhāraparinibbāyissa, tato mudutarāni sasaṅkhāraparinibbāyissa, tato mudutarāni uddhaṃsotaakaniṭṭhagāmissa vipassanindriyāni nāma. "
